magnificent mansion
Level-7th
CastingTime-1Minute
Range/Area-300ft
School-Conjuration
Attack/Save-div
OtherInfo-                You conjure an extradimensional dwelling in range that lasts for the duration. You choose where its one entrance is located. The entrance shimmers faintly and is 5 feet wide and 10 feet tall. You and any creature you designate when you cast the sell can enter the extradimensional dwelling as long as the ortal remains oen. You can oen or close the ortal if you are within 30 feet of it. While closed, the ortal is invisible.
